### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/v1
@token = your-admin-token-here

### ==============================================
### Reference Data Endpoints (9 Collections)
### ==============================================

### ==============================================
### 1. Focus Areas
### ==============================================

### Get All Focus Areas (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reference-data/focus-areas

# Expected Response (200):
# {
#   "success": true,
#   "data": [
#     {
#       "id": "...",
#       "name": "Technology",
#       "description": "Software development, IT, and tech innovation",
#       "icon": "💻",
#       "isActive": true
#     },
#     ...
#   ]
# }

### Get Focus Area by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/reference-data/focus-areas/focus-area-id-here

### Create Focus Area (Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/reference-data/focus-areas
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Design",
  "description": "Graphic design, UX/UI, and creative design",
  "icon": "🎨",
  "isActive": true
}

### Update Focus Area (Admin)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/reference-data/focus-areas/focus-area-id-here
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Updated description",
  "isActive": true
}

### Delete Focus Area (Admin)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/reference-data/focus-areas/focus-area-id-here
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ==============================================
### 2. Amenities
### ==============================================

### Get All Amenities
GET {{baseUrl}}/reference-data/amenities

# Expected Response:
# {
#   "success": true,
#   "data": [
#     {
#       "id": "...",
#       "name": "WiFi",
#       "description": "High-speed internet connection",
#       "icon": "📶",
#       "category": "connectivity"
#     },
#     ...
#   ]
# }

### Get Amenity by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/reference-data/amenities/amenity-id-here

### Create Amenity (Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/reference-data/amenities
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Parking",
  "description": "On-site parking facilities",
  "icon": "🅿️",
  "category": "convenience"
}

### Update Amenity (Admin)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/reference-data/amenities/amenity-id-here
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Updated parking description"
}

### Delete Amenity (Admin)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/reference-data/amenities/amenity-id-here
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ==============================================
### 3. Facilities
### ==============================================

### Get All Facilities
GET {{baseUrl}}/reference-data/facilities

### Create Facility (Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/reference-data/facilities
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Meeting Room",
  "description": "Professional meeting room with projector",
  "icon": "🏢",
  "category": "workspace",
  "capacity": 10
}

### ==============================================
### 4. Skills
### ==============================================

### Get All Skills
GET {{baseUrl}}/reference-data/skills

# Expected Response:
# {
#   "success": true,
#   "data": [
#     {
#       "id": "...",
#       "name": "JavaScript",
#       "category": "programming",
#       "focusAreaId": "technology-focus-area-id",
#       "level": "intermediate"
#     },
#     ...
#   ]
# }

### Create Skill (Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/reference-data/skills
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Python",
  "category": "programming",
  "focusAreaId": "technology-focus-area-id",
  "level": "beginner",
  "description": "Python programming language"
}

### Get Skills by Focus Area
GET {{baseUrl}}/reference-data/skills?focusAreaId=technology-focus-area-id

